that will drive consumers and suppliers to use the 
Budbo platform is the fact that it will encourage 
interactions between all parties and create value 
across channels. We achieve this by removing 
the burdensome signup process of existing 
platforms, as well as putting the match making 
power in the user’s control with a simple and 
streamlined interface.

Budbo’s major advantage over other platforms 
is that it does much more than simply utilize  
blockchain technology. Our platform is 
completely user-centric, which means users 
are and will remain at the heart of what we do. 

Our support for the cannabis community will 
be shown through transaction transparency 
and information sharing. We have created a 
complete technology solution that benefits 
dispensaries, growers, merchants, couriers and 
consumers in the blockchain.

The Budbo Token Sale will allow the user base to 
grow globally and create a global cannabis data 
exchange network.  The Budbo Token will be the 
API token that allows acess to the information 
grid and data flow within the Budbo ecosystem.

