time data, and geo-location of user, and 
proximity to dispensaries.

• Analytics ― Dispensaries can access 
real-time updates on targeted user likes, 
preferences, and products most likely to be 
purchased to improve their product offering 
and increase sales. With the use of the smart 
feature Grow Forecasting, they can meet 
dispensary demand ahead of time.

• User Interactions ― Users can interact in a 
fun, immersive environment on the Budbo 

platform. They can share reviews, play 
games, message and connect in one place.

• Retail Location Forecasting ― Startups 
